   <li><a href="#BSeleEditMoreWork">B. Selected Editions of More&rsquo;s Works</a></li>
   <li><a href="#CContBiog">C. Contemporary Biographies</a></li>
   <li><a href="#DBiogStud">D. Biographical Studies</a></li>
   <li><a href="#EGreeLatiWritCite">	E. Greek and Latin Writers Cited</a></li>
   <li><a href="#FSeleSecoStud">F. Selected Secondary Studies</a></li>
   <li><a href="#GBiblStud">G. Bibliographic Studies</a></li>
   </ul></li>
<li><a href="#Aca">Academic Tools</a></li>
