&amp; Uri Nodelman (eds.), URL =
 &lt;<a href="https://plato.stanford.edu/archives/fall2023/entries/thomas-more/">https://plato.stanford.edu/archives/fall2023/entries/thomas-more/</a>&gt;.
 [This was the previous entry on this topic in the <em>Stanford
